		Note: In most of the publications, author names are written in the alphabetical order.
		
		Notations:
		PA: Work as the primary or lead author.
		NPA: Work as the non-primary or non-lead author.
		EA: Equal contribution authorship.


Publication Summary: 
1. 6 IEEE or ACM Transaction papers as a primary author. 
2. 3 tier-1 conference papers (SIGMOD, VLDB, ICDE) as a primary author. 
3. 5 tier-2 conference papers (EDBT, IEEE NCA, ACM CODASPY, SSS) as a primary author or equal contribution, and IEEE NCA 2019 paper has received the best paper award. 
4. 3 tutorials as a primary author at IEEE ICDE, IEEE Big-Data, and ACM IWSPA.





